data.text:
List of all movies released in 2005, with film trailers when available. These movies of 2005 are listed alphabetically, but if you're looking for a particular film, you can search for it by using the Filter option below. This list includes some of the best movies of 2005, but since it's a list of all 2005 films there are also some bad movies on here as well. Additional information is also available for these 2005 movies, such as their directors, actors and taglines.

List ranges from Batman Begins to V for Vendetta and more.

If you're wondering, "What movies came out in 2005?" or "What are the best 2005 films?" then this list will answer your questions.

This is a comprehensive list of movies that premiered in 2005, so the films you see here range from smaller indie pictures to giant blockbusters. If you're a big cinema buff, this list is a great way to find some more obscure films that you may not already know. {#nodes}
